{
  "stem": "21731.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If he could get during the war some sweets, certainly I was the one who got it, not my brother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went always to their-- to my grandparents' flat, which was on the same floor, for the seder, for every Jewish holiday.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember special, after Yom Kippur, I waited for my grandfather, whose favorite I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't remember whether I mentioned that before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I waited for him outside the temple, and we walked home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And grandmother always had coffee and a cake ready for us to break the fast.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Coffee we were not allowed to get, but we got a piece of sugar dipped in coffee, which was our treat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then there was-- my grandfather died in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went there, I think, in 1916 together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We-- my brother and I went to Poland with my grandparents to stay at an estate of one of my uncles, and there we got really food.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because in Vienna, it was more or less hunger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not that we were hungry, but anyway, we didn't know what milk is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't know what cheese is, meat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Those things were nearly non-existent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had soups, and soups, and soups, and I hated that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we even fell ill on this estate, after getting the good food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because we were not used to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, after a month, my mother came to fetch us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the meantime, the Polish-Ukrainian war broke out, and it was very difficult to get any transport.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we got on a diplomatic train and stayed a few days in Warsaw, where I met the first time with my Warsaw family, which came in later handy.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
